<CountdownCircleTimer
  isRunning
  duration={totalSeconds}
  colors={['#004777', '#F7B801', '#A30000', '#A30000']}
  colorsTime={[7, 5, 2, 0]}
  style={{
    width: '200px', // Adjust this value as needed
    height: '200px', // Adjust this value as needed
  }}
>
  {/* Your countdown content */}
</CountdownCircleTimer>
